Made on September 2024 by Sunmyoung Yun.

This is my very basic game template for a 2D game. 

--------------------------------------------------------- HOW TO OPEN AND LAUNCH GAME

1)  Clone repo in VScode
2)  Type "make" in VScode terminal ("Should automatically download brew, sfml and fmt in this stage")
3)  Type "run" in VScode terminal

- Type "make clean" to removed build
- Type "make" to make build
- Type "run" to run build

--------------------------------------------------------- CODE STRUCTURE
/sfml_game_template
│
├── /.vscode                                            # VSCode settings and configurations
│
├── /src                                                # Source files
│   ├── main.cpp                                        # Main entry point of the game
│   │
│   ├── /game                                           # Core engine functionalities
│   │   ├── game.cpp                                    # Game loop and game state management
│   │   ├── game.hpp
│   │   │
│   │   ├── /constants                                  # Constants 
│   │   │   ├── constants.cpp
│   │   │   └── constants.hpp
│   │   │
│   │   ├── /flags                                      # Flags and state indicators
│   │   │   ├── flags.cpp
│   │   │   └── flags.hpp
│   │   │
│   │   ├── /physics                                    # Physics and collision detection
│   │   │   ├── physics.cpp
│   │   │   └── physics.hpp
│   │   │
│   │   ├── /rendering                                  # SFML window and view 
│   │   │   ├── window.cpp
│   │   │   └── window.hpp
│   │   │
│   │   ├── /utils                                      # Utility functions and classes
│   │   │   ├── utils.cpp
│   │   │   └── utils.hpp
│   │   │
│   │   ├── /scenes                                     # Scene management
│   │   │   ├── scenes.cpp
│   │   │   └── scenes.hpp
│   
├── /assets                                             # Game assets
│   ├── /fonts                                          # Font files
│   │   ├── /ttf                                        # TrueType font files
│   │   │   └── font1.ttf
│   │   ├── fonts.cpp                                   # Font-related source file 
│   │   └── fonts.hpp                                   # Font-related header file 
│   │
│   ├── /sound                                          # Sound effects
│   │   ├── /mp3                                        # MP3 files
│   │   ├── /wav                                        # WAV files
│   │   │   └── bgm.mp3                                 # Example background music file
│   │   ├── sound.cpp                                   # Sound-related source file 
│   │   └── sound.hpp                                   # Sound-related header file 
│   │
│   ├── /sprites                                        # Sprite images
│   │   ├── /png                                        # PNG files
│   │   │   └── background.png
│   │   ├── sprites.cpp                                 # Sprite-related source file 
│   │   └── sprites.hpp                                 # Sprite-related header file 
│  
├── /libs                   
│   ├── /SFML                                       #need to add sfml package config later
│   ├── /SPDLOG                                     #need to add spdlog configuration later
│   │
│   ├── /logging                                         # spdlog for logging 
│   │   ├── log.cpp
│   │   └── log.hpp
│   │   ├── errors.txt
│   │   └── info.txt
│ 
├── /.coderabbit.yaml                                   # Coderabbit configuration file (if applicable)
│
├── /.gitignore                                         # Git ignore file
│
├── /Makefile                                           # Makefile for building the project
│
└── README.md                                           # Project documentation

